-Members of Divest Harvard have pointed out the hypocrisy of educational institutions like Harvard using their money
to support industries that threaten the future of their students
by causing global warming. They also make the argument that fossil fuel investments put Harvard’s endowment at great risk.

-Noting the widespread agreement that setting a price on carbon is the most effective approach
